like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T22:19:15.000Z","msg":"住酒店好悶(除左扑野)，反而hostel 好多好有特色，設計幾好，睇留言簿好多都好好笑"},{"pid":"df50329feedc826f92aa122137ceb4d0ee9a420a","tid":846082,"uid":91272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T23:17:47.000Z","msg":"識人在此<br />\neveryone is interesting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8de967a125b7d36a378f597a4168cfbd5764b4e","tid":846082,"uid":49702,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:41:06.000Z","msg":"歐洲d hostel真係好大好有特色<br />\n特別有廚房同好大個public area果類<br />\n你敢上前搭嗲係會識到人<br />\n<br />\n大陸果d好多都係得間房<br />\n就真係純住/識房入面果個<br />\n<br />\n早幾日自己去東歐20日 <br />\n有一半時間都係同新識既人去玩"},{"pid":"2a361402855cd31a9080bafa3a158a41450339d7","tid":846082,"uid":34654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"鐘意airbnb有洗衣機同廚房可以煮下野食<br />\n例如去日本可以買牛返去煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7316c3a9c6b86108d512a3a769aff937f335dbbf","tid":846082,"uid":34654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:46:35.000Z","msg":"鐘意airbnb有洗衣機同廚房可以煮下野食<br />\n例如去日本可以買牛返去煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f645497444d8178b02eebaad514f3b09cf72f67","tid":846082,"uid":51747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:51:07.000Z","msg":"couchsurfing就話識host啫，airbnb變晒質啦"},{"pid":"ff4df438187ca9d1d25af64669fb023c614b9c86","tid":846082,"uid":86948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"why not both"},{"pid":"f53e47c68529dd2af8c645688c569d3df5c2fc1d","tid":846082,"uid":204531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"講真 以前就得 而家自從有左smart phone, 個個返到房都係玩電話"},{"pid":"ab351e4e709e6a34f9cb374d51d75f29c